headline: DoorDash : NYC Delivery Pay Rule Slashes Jobs for Thousands of New Yorkers
summary: New data reveals that in the one year since New York City enacted its minimum pay rules for food delivery workers, thousands of Dashers across the City have been left out from the benefits this rule...
